Franky, also known as “Iron Man” Franky, is the shipwright of the Straw Hat Pirates and one of the Senior Officers of the Straw Hat Grand Fleet in the popular manga and anime series One Piece. He is a 36-year-old cyborg from Water 7 and was introduced as the leader of the Franky Family, a group of ship dismantlers. Franky is a skilled shipwright who has built several notable ships, including the Thousand Sunny, the current ship of the Straw Hat Pirates. He is known for his unique appearance, which includes a cyborg body and a love for cola, and his ability to repair and build ships with incredible speed and skill.
